	<description>
  		The Diasparsoft Toolkit contains utilities not found in Java or
	  	other well-known utility packages. It includes extensions to the
	  	language, extensions to JUnit and other testing utilities. We
        developed these utilities while writing the book
        JUnit Recipes: Practical Programmer Testing Methods.
	</description>
	<shortDescription>A toolkit for Java programmers</shortDescription>

